OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying dry
OL,6,Fthis evening and overnight with
OL,7,Fprolonged clear spells for most.
OL,8,FPatchy mist and fog reforming, though
OL,9,Fmore isolated than the previous night.
OL,10,FChilly, particularly for rural areas.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FA bright start to Thursday
OL,13,Fas fog patches clear. Cloud gradually
OL,14,Fbuilding into the afternoon but
OL,15,Fstaying dry. Another very mild day
OL,16,Fwith light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
